INSERT INTO
			  Records (
			    filter_id,
			    styles,
			    teleports,
			    time,
			    player_id,
			    server_id,
			    bhops,
			    perfs,
			    perfect_perfs,
			    plugin_version_id
			  )
			VALUES
			  (
			    (
			      SELECT
				id
			      FROM
				CourseFilters
			      WHERE
				course_id = ?
				AND mode = ?
				AND teleports = ?
			      LIMIT
				1
			    ), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?
			  )
